    "We refer to this metric as the unfamiliarity score of a query.",
    "We consider a finetuning example to be unfamiliar if the unfamiliarity score of its query is above a certain threshold.",
    "In this section, we investigate the underlying mechanisms that govern how finetuned LLMs hallucinate.",
    "We hypothesize that, when face with unfamiliar inputs, model predictions mimic the responses associated with the model's unfamiliar finetuning examples.",
